These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: almond-milk, 7up, fanta, coffee
Sport: sailing, snowboarding, rowing, surfing
1. Beverage:almond-milk is on the right of Sport:rowing##1
2. Sport:surfing is on the far left##1
3. Sport:rowing is between Sport:snowboarding and Beverage:7up##2
4. Beverage:coffee is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:fanta is between Beverage:7up and Beverage:almond-milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | coffee         | 7up   | fanta | almond-milk       |
| Sport      | surfing | sailing | rowing   | snowboarding |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
