3. Nationality:spanish is on the right of Nationality:thai##1
4. Hobby:writing is on the left of Nationality:thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | writing | rock-climbing | traveling |
| Nationality   | italian    | chinese   | thai | spanish       |

